    <title>PKE kernel labs</title>
    <link href="http://peacewang017.github.io/2024/03/17/PKE-kernel-labs/"/>
    <id>http://peacewang017.github.io/2024/03/17/PKE-kernel-labs/</id>
    <published>2024-03-16T17:24:55.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-03-16T17:24:55.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="1-做了什么"><a href="#1-做了什么" class="headerlink" title="1. 做了什么"></a>1. 做了什么</h1><p>上学期完成了一些基于 RISC-V 指令集的 PKE(Proxy Kernel for Education) 操作系统内核的基础实验，这学期的课程设计要求完成后面的挑战部分。实验的代码和文档如下：</p><pre><code>1. 代码：https://gitee.com/hustos/riscv-pke2. 文档：https://gitee.com/hustos/pke-doc3. 我的完成源码：https://github.com/peacewang017/OS_labs</code></pre><p>实验其实仍然是完善一些系统调用，不过比上学期的要复杂和个性化许多，本篇主要记载一些自己实验时遇到的坑点和待完善的部分。</p><h1 id="2-笔记"><a href="#2-笔记" class="headerlink" title="2. 笔记"></a>2. 笔记</h1><h2 id="2-1-lab1-challenge2-errorline"><a href="#2-1-lab1-challenge2-errorline" class="headerlink" title="2.1 lab1_challenge2 errorline"></a>2.1 lab1_challenge2 errorline</h2><p>实际上与打印用户调用栈相同，会读ELF文件即可。</p><h3 id="ELF-结构"><a href="#ELF-结构" class="headerlink" title="ELF 结构"></a>ELF 结构</h3><p>ELF有两种视图：链接(link)视图和执行(execute)视图，在两种视图下有两个不同的节头表(section header table)，分别指向链接视图下的节(section)和执行视图下的段(segment)。</p><p><img src="/2024/03/17/PKE-kernel-labs/ELF.png" alt="alt text"></p><p>有趣的是，在 ELF 中，所有字符串都用一个 Elf_32_word 变量来表示，这个变量的值是该字符串在符号表(strtab)中的偏移量，所以我们先取出 strtab 。</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">elf_status <span class="title function_">elf_load</span><span class="params">(elf_ctx *ctx)</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// elf_prog_header structure is defined in kernel/elf.h</span></span><br><span class="line">    elf_prog_header ph_addr;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> i, off;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// traverse the elf program segment headers</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> (i = <span class="number">0</span>, off = ctx-&gt;ehdr.phoff; i &lt; ctx-&gt;ehdr.phnum; i++, off += <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(ph_addr)) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// read segment headers</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (elf_fpread(ctx, (<span class="type">void</span> *)&amp;ph_addr, <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(ph_addr), off) != <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(ph_addr)) <span class="keyword">return</span> EL_EIO;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (ph_addr.type != ELF_PROG_LOAD) <span class="keyword">continue</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (ph_addr.memsz &lt; ph_addr.filesz) <span class="keyword">return</span> EL_ERR;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (ph_addr.vaddr + ph_addr.memsz &lt; ph_addr.vaddr) <span class="keyword">return</span> EL_ERR;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// allocate memory block before elf loading</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">void</span> *dest = elf_alloc_mb(ctx, ph_addr.vaddr, ph_addr.vaddr, ph_addr.memsz);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// actual loading</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> (elf_fpread(ctx, dest, ph_addr.memsz, ph_addr.off) != ph_addr.memsz)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> EL_EIO;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// 读文件用buf</span></span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// find strtab header</span></span><br><span class="line">    uint64 strtab_sh_off = ctx-&gt;ehdr.shoff + ctx-&gt;ehdr.shstrndx * <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(elf_sect_header);</span><br><span class="line">    elf_sect_header strtab_sh;</span><br><span class="line">    elf_fpread(ctx, (<span class="type">void</span>*)(&amp;strtab_sh), <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(elf_sect_header), strtab_sh_off);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// find strtab</span></span><br><span class="line">    uint64 strtab_off = strtab_sh.offset;</span><br><span class="line">    uint64 strtab_size = strtab_sh.size;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">char</span> strtab[strtab_size];</span><br><span class="line">    elf_fpread(ctx, (<span class="type">void</span>*)strtab, strtab_size, strtab_off);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// traverse to find debugline header</span></span><br><span class="line">    elf_sect_header debugline_sh;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="type">int</span> index = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span>(; index &lt; ctx-&gt;ehdr.shnum; index++)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        uint64 this_sh_off = ctx-&gt;ehdr.shoff + index * <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(elf_sect_header);</span><br><span class="line">        elf_fpread(ctx, (<span class="type">void</span>*)(&amp;debugline_sh), <span class="keyword">sizeof</span>(elf_sect_header), this_sh_off);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="built_in">strcmp</span>(<span class="string">&quot;.debug_line&quot;</span>, strtab + debugline_sh.name) == <span class="number">0</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(index == ctx-&gt;ehdr.shnum)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">        sprint(<span class="string">&quot;section &#x27;.debug_line&#x27; not found in elf\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// find debugline</span></span><br><span class="line">    uint64 debugline_off = debugline_sh.offset;</span><br><span class="line">    uint64 debugline_size = debugline_sh.size;</span><br><span class="line">    elf_fpread(ctx, (<span class="type">void</span>*)debugline, debugline_size, debugline_off);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">// call make_addr_line</span></span><br><span class="line">    make_addr_line(ctx, debugline, debugline_size);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> EL_OK;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>接着，按照 PKE 的进程和文件组织方法进行后续处理，这里不再赘述。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
